{{Infobox journal | title = Peregrine: American Immigration in the 21st Century | image = <!-- or |cover= --> | image_size = | alt = | caption = | former_name = <!-- or |former_names= --> | abbreviation = <!-- ISO 4 abbreviation --> | bluebook = <!-- For law journals only --> | discipline = <!-- or |subject= --> | peer-reviewed = | language = English | editor = [[Tim Kane]] | publisher = [[Hoover Institution]] | country = United States | history = 2014 to 2015 | frequency = | openaccess = | license = | impact = | impact-year = | ISSNlabel = | ISSN = | eISSN = | CODEN = | JSTOR = | LCCN = | OCLC = | website = https://www.hoover.org/publications/peregrine | link1 = | link1-name = | link2 = <!-- up to |link5= --> | link2-name = <!-- up to |link5-name= --> | boxwidth = }}
'''''Peregrine: American Immigration in the 21st Century''''' is an [[online journal]] published by the [[Hoover Institution]] as part of its Conte Initiative on Immigration Reform.<ref name=official>{{cite web|url=http://www.hoover.org/publications/peregrine|title = Peregrine: American Immigration in the 21st Century|publisher = [[Hoover Institution]]|accessdate = July 2, 2014}}</ref><ref name=cnbc>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnbc.com/id/101785280|title = The Hoover Institution Launches Online Journal About Immigration Reform|date = June 24, 2014|accessdate = July 2, 2014|publisher = [[CNBC]]}}</ref> It is focused on understanding [[immigration to the United States]] and identifying optimal immigration policy for the contemporary United States. The journal is [[Editor-in-chief|edited]] by economist [[Tim Kane]] and relies on contributions from Hoover's Working Group on Immigration Reform, co-chaired by Kane and [[Edward Lazear]].<ref name=official/>
==History==
The first issue of ''Peregrine'', issue 1401, was published in late June 2014.<ref name=official/> ==Reception==
The news release by the Hoover Institution about the launch was published on ''[[CNBC]]'',<ref name=cnbc/> and [[The Herald (Rock Hill)|Herald Online]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.heraldonline.com/2014/06/24/6086336/the-hoover-institution-launches.html |title=The Hoover Institution Launches Online Journal About Immigration Reform |date=June 24, 2014 |accessdate=July 2, 2014 |publisher=[[The Herald (Rock Hill)|Herald Online]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140706173048/http://www.heraldonline.com/2014/06/24/6086336/the-hoover-institution-launches.html |archivedate=July 6, 2014 |df= }}</ref>
